      "side": 1,
      "message": "To elaborate, here\u0027s the sysroot that the kernel build is using for building host binaries, prior to this change:\n\nhttps://cs.android.com/android/kernel/superproject/+/common-android-mainline:prebuilts/gcc/linux-x86/host/x86_64-linux-glibc2.17-4.8/sysroot/\n\nShould I change it to:\n\nhttps://cs.android.com/android/kernel/superproject/+/common-android-mainline:prebuilts/ndk-r26/toolchains/llvm/prebuilt/linux-x86_64/sysroot/\n\n?",
